  npcVisitFlavors:
  - speaks of patterns in the marsh that took years to understand.
  - shows you a half-finished piece of weaving. The geometry is intricate and strange.
  - is more talkative than usual, the work going well.
  npcExchangeFlavors:
  - wraps a piece of honeycomb in a reed leaf and tucks it in your pack.
  - presses a small woven charm into your hands — more care in it than it looks like.
  buildingDilapidatedName: Sagging Drying House
